We recommended that Management take the following courses of action:

Enhance project implementation and monitoring to avoid delays;

Submit the Bid Documents and any subsequent documents relative to the construction of SWMRF;
Henceforth, comply strictly to the provisions of R.A. No. 9184 and its IRR in addressing delays in the fulfillment of the contract caused by contractors.

We recommended that Management take the following courses of action:
Verify the amounts mentioned above and ensure that appropriate adjusting entries are made in order to correct the affected account balances in the FS as at December 31, 2018;
